                  <persName id="t17970426-18-person189">
                  ANN
                   LACON
               <interp inst="t17970426-18-person189" type="surname" value="LACON"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970426-18-person189" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970426-18-person189" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - Q. What relation is Mr. 
               <persName id="t17970426-18-person190">
                  John
                   Lacon
               <interp inst="t17970426-18-person190" type="surname" value="Lacon"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970426-18-person190" type="given" value="John"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17970426-18-person190" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             to you? - A. He is my husband: I lost some property in the month of March last, I don't know the exact time, there were several articles. I am a milliner and mantua-maker; the prisoner at the bar lodged in our house about eight weeks.</p>
               <p>Q. Did she follow any business in your house? - A. Yes; she followed the business of a mantua-maker; she had nothing to do with my business, she was paid for her work.</p>
               <p>Q. How came you to know she had robbed you? - A. I found the duplicates upon her; the pawnbroker has got part of them.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179704260023"></xptr>WILLIAM BAKER sworn. - I am a pawnbroker; I know the prisoner at the bar, she has brought, generally, articles to my shop to pledge; I have got the things that she pawned with me (produces the articles); I received these things from the prisoner.</p>
               <p>Mrs. Lacon. These goods I lost; I can positively swear that I lost them from time to time.</p>
               <p>The prisoner called two witnesses, who gave her a good character.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17970426-18-verdict96" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17970426-18-verdict96" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. (Aged 32.)</p>
